OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780668674
OL,3,CThreatened Gloucestershire lido will
OL,4,Creopen this summer
OL,6,FStroud District Council has committed
OL,7,Fto reopening the town's historic
OL,8,Foutdoor swimming pool this summer.
OL,10,FAt a meeting on the evening of
OL,11,FWednesday, 3 June, councillors
OL,12,Funanimously voted to approve an
OL,13,Fadditional #276,000 of funding to
OL,14,Fcarry out essential repairs to the 90-
OL,15,Fyear-old lido, on top of more than
OL,16,F#200,000 already set aside.
OL,18,FCouncillors say the money is from
OL,19,Fprevious years, where they underspent
OL,20,Fon their lido budget.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
