FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780668674
OL,3,CThreatened Gloucestershire lido will
OL,4,Creopen this summer
OL,6,FThe future of the pool was thrown into
OL,7,Fdoubt after a safety assessment in
OL,8,FFebruary 2026 found significant
OL,9,Fstructural problems. The council
OL,10,Festimated repairs would cost around
OL,11,Ffive million pounds, which it said it
OL,12,Fcouldn't afford.
OL,14,FA campaign group was set up in protest
OL,15,Fof the decision. Campaigners argued
OL,16,Fthere was a more realistic plan to
OL,17,Freopen the pool for a fraction of the
OL,18,Fcost, in the short term.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
