OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780668674
OL,3,CThreatened Gloucestershire lido will
OL,4,Creopen this summer
OL,6,FCommunity protests, a competition, and
OL,7,Fa petition signed by more than 4,000
OL,8,Fpeople followed.
OL,10,FLocal voices supporting the campaign
OL,11,Fincluded Mary Portas, Edith Bowman and
OL,12,FDale Vince.
OL,14,FSpeaking at the meeting last night,
OL,15,FDarren Young, the council's leisure
OL,16,Fservices manager, said the funds would
OL,17,Fbe used to help the historic site
OL,18,Freopen rather than being used for "a
OL,19,Ffull refurbishment".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
