PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780668674
OL,3,CThreatened Gloucestershire lido will
OL,4,Creopen this summer
OL,6,FThe council hopes the lido can reopen
OL,7,Fby the middle of August.
OL,9,F"They listened"
OL,11,FThe campaign group Save Stroud Lido
OL,12,Fsays the decision demonstrates the
OL,13,Fstrength of community support and
OL,14,Fmarks the beginning of work to secure
OL,15,Fthe lido's long-term future.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
