CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780668674
OL,3,CThreatened Gloucestershire lido will
OL,4,Creopen this summer
OL,6,FIn a Facebook post after the meeting,
OL,7,Fa spokesperson said: "They (the
OL,8,Fcouncil) listened to the community and
OL,9,Fto engineering experts who showed
OL,10,Fthere was a realistic plan to reopen
OL,11,Fthe pool for a fraction of the
OL,12,Foriginally proposed #5 million cost.
OL,14,F"Councillors asked some tough
OL,15,Fquestions ` rightly so ` but they also
OL,16,Frecognised the enormous health,
OL,17,Fwellbeing and community value of
OL,18,Fgetting the pool open again and
OL,19,Fprotecting it for future generations.
OL,26,@oD@\pmpD@Hpn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
