PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780668674
OL,3,CThreatened Gloucestershire lido will
OL,4,Creopen this summer
OL,6,F"We are absolutely delighted by last
OL,7,Fnight's decision and can't wait to see
OL,8,Ffamilies, swimmers and young people
OL,9,Fenjoying the Lido again this summer.
OL,11,F"And now the focus turns to getting
OL,12,Fthe works completed and the gates
OL,13,Freopened as quickly as possible.
OL,15,F"Because this is more than a pool.
OL,17,F"It's part of Stroud's identity. A
OL,18,Fplace for fun, friendships, exercise,
OL,19,Fmemories and safe outdoor swimming for
OL,20,Fgenerations to come."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
